text: Laurent Lacasa (born 28 September 1964) is a French rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
